General Information

Vitamin D capsules

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet

Common Uses

Vitamin D is mainly produced in our skin by a reaction that requires sunlight. People who limit their exposure to sunlight may have an increased need for Vitamin D supplementation. Vitamin D assists calcium absorption and support calcium balance in the body

Ingredients

Colecalciferol (Vitamin D3 1000IU)

Directions

Take 1 capsule daily with food or as directed by your healthcare professional
